Package: remis
Title: Interact with the UNFCCC Data Interface API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexander", "Hurley", , "agl.hurley@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9641-2805"))
Description: Functions for exploring and downloading data sets using the Flexible Query
  from UNFCCC's Data Interface. Currently Annex-One and Non-Annex-One sources are
  supported.
